lead_paragraph: The Cincinnati Reds haven't had a whole lot to celebrate recently, which is why they took a little extra satisfaction in how they ended their five-game losing streak.

headline.print_headline: Reds End Skid With 4-3 Win Over Pirates on Peraza's Sac Fly
